This file is part of Chalks.

What is Chalks ?
--------------
Chalks is a software under development for crossplatform realtime concurrent editing.
The primary focus will be ease of use and minimum requirements.

Chalks is written in Nermerle, using the Mono platform http://go-mono.com
Chalks, Nermele and Mono are open source multiplatform projects.

Chalks 2003, 2004, 2005.
http://chalks.berlios.de



Features
--------

- Server/Client architecture, ultra easy usage
- Full crossplatform (inherited from Mono)

Release Status
--------------

Still in planning/design phase

